F,F,F%F," }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 114 "Both answers are correct, t
hey represent the same indefinite integral, I personally prefer the on
e we get by hand." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 95 "Now we'll do some mo
