can compute double integrals just as easily as we computed mixed deriv
atives.  Compute the following multiple integration: " }}{EXCHG {PARA 
0 "> " 0 "" {XPPEDIT 19 1 "int(int(x*y+x^3-y^2+2,x),y);" "6#-%$intG6$-
